ioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/><w>ἔπτά</w></mentioned> и т. д. Ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_ævdæm"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævddæs"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævdaj"/></xr>.%n<bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 50, 75</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>48</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>25</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref target="#ref_Преображенский"/><biblScope>21, 38, 167, 213, 231</biblScope></bibl>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Like other numerals, belongs to the Iranian heritage; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>haft</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/><w>avd</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/><w>*avd(ʼβt)</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xln"><lang/><w>αβδα</w></mentioned> (in <mentioned xml:lang="xln"><lang/><w>’Aρδάβδα</w></mentioned>, literally “(city) of seven gods”), <mentioned xml:lang="ydg"><lang/><w>avdoh</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sgh"><lang/><w>ūvd, ūft</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="mnj"><lang/><w>ōvdá</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>haṷda</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>hapta-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>sapta-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/><w>ἔπτά</w></mentioned> etc. Cf. <xr><ref target="#entry_ævdæm"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævddæs"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævdaj"/></xr>.%n<bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 50, 75</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>48</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>25</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref target="#ref_Преображенский"/><biblScope>21, 38, 167, 213, 231</biblScope></bibl>.</etym></entry>